      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "フォーッフォフォ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ho ho ho…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6666666667,
      "endTime": 6.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "わしこそがサンタの中のサンタ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am the Santa of all Santas…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5,
      "endTime": 9.692307550199999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ファーファッファ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ho ho ho…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8666666667,
      "endTime": 12.1333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "わしのプレゼントが火を吹くぞい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My presents breathe fire…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.14,
      "endTime": 15.24,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 15.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……ちょっと、やっぱり設定おかしいわよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You know‚ this just feels so wrong after all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4666666667,
      "endTime": 19.0696926594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すみれ、怯えてるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire’s freaked out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0696926594,
      "endTime": 21.1157266632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 21.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おっかしいなぁ〜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s weird…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3,
      "endTime": 23.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こんなはずやなかったんやけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It shouldn’t go like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0333333333,
      "endTime": 25.9224531545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 26.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "あの〜……どちらさまでしょうか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello? Who’s there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1,
      "endTime": 30.514240169500003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 30.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "いい子にしてたすみれちゃんに\n瑠依サンタと優サンタがプレゼントを持ってきたで～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because you’ve been so good‚ Sumire-chan‚\nSanta Rui and Santa Yu have brought you presents.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7333333333,
      "endTime": 36.524411028399996,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 133.33333339999953
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 36.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃん！？　瑠依ちゃん！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan…?! Rui-chan?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7,
      "endTime": 39.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 39.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "三人で食べようと思ってケーキも買ってきたわよ\n手作りケーキという訳にはいかなかったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We brought a cake‚ so we can all eat together.\nIt’s not handmade or anything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3333333333,
      "endTime": 46.4282583709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 46.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "手作りケーキって……もしかして二人とも\n私がパーティーの準備をしていたことを知ってたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Handmade cake… Did you two know\nI was preparing a party?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6,
      "endTime": 54.4824713022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 54.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "元人気子役の名演技でもうちらの目はごまかされへんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even the famed acting skills of the former child actress can’t fool us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7,
      "endTime": 59.456304073300004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 59.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "私達の絆を甘く見ないでほしいわ\nすみれの考えなんてお見通しに決まってるでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t underestimate the bond between us.\nWe can see through what you were thinking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6333333333,
      "endTime": 66.2556914509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "ケーキ作ってるのを見ても全然気付けへんかったんやで\nこんなこと言うてるけど、すみれちゃんが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You didn’t catch on at all.\nYou say that‚ but even seeing Sumire-chan making a cake‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.4333333333,
      "endTime": 73.4490247615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 73.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと優！\nそれは今言わなくてもいいでしょ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a minute Yu-chan!\nYou don’t have to say that now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.6333333333,
      "endTime": 77.64999996830001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 77.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……二人とも知ってたんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… You both knew…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8333333333,
      "endTime": 82.2706576665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 82.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、すみれ？　どうして泣いてるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Sumire-chan? Why are you crying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.4666666667,
      "endTime": 86.29950119659999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 86.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "優、あなたがサプライズしようなんて言うから\nすみれが泣いちゃったじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan‚ you said let’s surprise Sumire-chan‚ and\nnow you made her cry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5333333333,
      "endTime": 91.2653739892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんだってそんな格好して\nノリノリやったやんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t chalk it all up on me. You were totally in on it\ndressing up like that‚ Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.4333333333,
      "endTime": 95.47242615639999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 95.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "違うの、二人は何も悪くないの\nこれは嬉しくて泣いてるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ you two didn’t do anything wrong.\nThese tears are because I’m so happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6666666667,
      "endTime": 102.7000905953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 102.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "二人のサプライズがすっごく嬉しくて泣いてるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m crying because I’m so happy about your surprise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9,
      "endTime": 106.9973468304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 107.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "喜んでくれたんなら良かったわぁ\nふふっ。すみれちゃんの顔かわええなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m glad we could make you happy.\nHehehe. Sumire-chan‚ your face is so cute…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.2,
      "endTime": 114.50044255930001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
