      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "せやで\nすみれちゃんにはいつも驚かされっぱなしや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true.\nWe’re always getting surprised by you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.6666666667,
      "endTime": 241.9962126389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 242.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、優ちゃん……\n二人にそう言ってもらえるのが最高のプレゼントだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan… Yu-chan…\nHearing you say that is the best present I could want.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.2,
      "endTime": 249.4705145369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 250.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "どう、すみれ。今年のクリスマスは楽しい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ Sumire-chan‚ was this year’s Christmas fun?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 251.5,
      "endTime": 255.1367574215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "うん、すっごく楽しい！　どんなクリスマスになるか\n準備をしながら何度も想像したけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ so much fun. While I was getting ready‚\nI kept imagining how it would be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.3333333333,
      "endTime": 263.38382697730003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 263.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "今夜は想像の何倍も楽しくて\n忘れられないクリスマスになったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But tonight was way more fun than anything I imagined.\nIt turned out to be an unforgettable Christmas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.5666666667,
      "endTime": 269.1420455442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 269.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_05-smr021.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスを大好きな人と一緒に過ごせるって\nこんなに素敵で幸せなことなんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Spending Christmas together with the people you care about\nis such a wonderfully happy thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.3333333333,
      "endTime": 276.5735919281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 276.7666666667
